source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_001<tab>Lali-just the sinner I've been looking for-ho.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_001<tab>Ah, l'<var 08 E905 ((étrangère)) ((étranger)) /var>, tu tombes bien. J'ai un cadeau pour toi.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_002<tab>Another one of those recording devices has arrived from Konogg. Seems the lad has more he wants to say to you. Here.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_002<tab>Ça vient de Konogg, c'est encore un de ces appareils bizarres. À croire qu'il avait encore des confidences à te faire.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_003<tab>When you have a moment, be sure to see what's on it.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_003<tab>Oublie pas d'y jeter un œil quand t'auras le temps.
TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_GLAGG_000_004<tab>(-???-)Le porion et l'<var 08 E905 ((étrangère)) ((étranger)) /var>... toujours fourrés ensemble, vous deux<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_GLAGG_100_004<tab>Yes, the two of you! What are you doin', talkin' and noddin' suspiciously!? What are you up to!?
TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_GLAGG_000_005<tab><gasp> You're conspirin' to take over the village, aren't you!? Just like those murderous machines!
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_GLAGG_000_005<tab>Je sais<var 1D /var>: vous voulez devenir doyens à la place du doyen, c'est ça<var 1D /var>!? Prendre le village par la force, comme ces saletés d'androïdes<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_GLAGG_000_006<tab>Huh? What am I...? What did I just...? Unnngh, my head...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_GLAGG_000_006<tab>Ah... Euh... P-pardon, je sais pas ce qui m'a pris de dire ça. Oubliez.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_007<tab>Something's not right with Glagg. And it's not quite the same sort of “not right” what follows a few too many casks of ale...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_007<tab>Ouah... Le doyen est en train de perdre salement les pédales. J'espère que ça va aller...

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_008<tab>Well, whatever it is, it's nothing you need to worry about. I'll take care of it.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_008<tab>T'en fais pas pour lui, je suis sûr qu'il s'en remettra. Au pire, j'irai lui dire un mot.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_009<tab>Now then, was there something else you needed?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_009<tab>Au fait, qu'est-ce qui t'amène<var 1D /var>? Tu voulais me demander quelque chose<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_A1_000_001<tab>Is there anything I can help with?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_A1_000_001<tab>Je peux encore me rendre utile<var 1D /var>?
TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_A1_000_002<tab>La recon<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion du village avance bien<var 1D /var>?
TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_VILLAGERB03954_000_012<tab>(-???-)Psst. Je peux vous parler une minute<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_013<tab>You... What do you want? If you're here to mock us, have done with it and leave us be.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_013<tab>Quoi, qu'est-ce qu'on a fait de mal, encore<var 1D /var>!? Z'êtes pas contents qu'on rebâtisse le village, c'est ça<var 1D /var>? Vous préférez l'ancienne déco<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_VILLAGERB03954_000_014<tab>N-No, I'm not here to mock you. On the contrary, I want to join you.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_VILLAGERB03954_000_014<tab>Non, non, pas du tout<var 1D /var>! C'est même tout le contraire. En fait, je voudrais vous donner un coup de main, moi aussi.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_VILLAGERB03954_000_015<tab>I'm usually not one to get involved, preferring to observe from a safe distance while making the occasional comment to remind people of my presence. But seeing how hard you've been working for the village, I couldn't help but want to make myself useful for a change.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_VILLAGERB03954_000_015<tab>Je me dis en toute modestie qu'un Nain clairvoyant comme moi serait un sacré atout pour votre équipe.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_016<tab>Well, we could certainly use all the help we can get... What say you, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>? Shall we welcome him to the crew?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_016<tab>Hm. Un volontaire de plus, ça se refuse pas. Et je suis sûr que l'<var 08 E905 ((étrangère)) ((étranger)) /var> est d'accord avec moi.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_VILLAGERB03954_000_017<tab>Thank you! I'm certain you won't regret it!
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_VILLAGERB03954_000_017<tab>Merci à vous deux. Je vais me donner à fond, faites-moi confiance.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_018<tab>After that strangeness with Glagg, I wasn't sure what to expect from our dour friend, but it sure wasn't an offer of help.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_018<tab>Bon, je vais voir quelles tâches je peux confier à notre ami “le clairvoyant”.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_019<tab>Anyway, I'll find a moment to talk with the fellow about our plans. And when he's managed to settle in, you ought to have a word with him too.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_019<tab>Dès qu'il sera fixé, tu pourras aller lui proposer ton aide.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_DWARFMASTER03671_000_020<tab>But to answer your earlier question─there's nothing we need you for right now. Only a matter of time before we call on you again, though, so kick your feet up while you can.
TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_SYSTEM_000_023<tab>A weekly quest which continues the story is now available from the dour dwarf in Komra.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_SYSTEM_000_023<tab>Vous pouvez à présent lancer des quêtes hebdomadaires permettant de faire avancer l'histoire en vous adressant au villageois présomptueux.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_SYSTEM_000_024<tab>Lend your aid and help the dwarves of Komra to rebuild their home.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_SYSTEM_000_024<tab>Prêtez-lui main-forte, et contribuez ainsi à la recon<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion de Komra<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_SYSTEM_000_031<tab>The message can be viewed in your <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Portable Archive<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, which is available under Collection in the Duty section of the main menu.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA512_04045_SYSTEM_000_031<tab>Les messages de Konogg sont au<var 16 /var>to<var 16 /var>ma<var 16 /var>ti<var 16 /var>que<var 16 /var>ment consignés dans l'enregistreur de données d'Anogg, accessible en sélectionnant “Objets précieux” depuis la rubrique Missions du menu principal.
